The paper proposes a novel data hiding technique for images, which falls under the category of information hiding and cryptography. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves mathematical modeling and analysis, which suggests the possibility of it being categorized under cs.MM (Mathematical Modeling), cs.IT (Information Theory), or cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). Finally, the proposed technique involves image processing and manipulation, which could place it under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
